name: RingRunnerz
description:
10000 Intergalactic Outlaws looking to conquer and take over 
on Polygon. The Ring Runnerz, players will embark on an epic journey through thrilling seasons. Season 1 sets the stage for an adrenaline-fueled launch phase, where participants dive into a dynamic virtual universe. Players will be rewarded with tokens for their dedication and accomplishments. Brace yourself for intense competition as prize pool competitions offer enticing rewards, including rare artifacts and exclusive bonuses that propel players to reach new heights.
